@node "Sicherheit" "Sicherheit"

                        @{b}@{u}Protection advices@{ub}@{uu}

           @{b}DANGER:@{ub} This tool works only with @{b}@{u}one@{ub}@{uu} of the
            ECS versions of UFO. One version and the AGA version
            use a lot of files (base.dat,soldier.dat...) to save
            the data. For these versions you find a lot of tools in
            the Aminet. To use my tool you need the version which
            save all data to one file with the length of @{b}45299 Byte@{ub}
            and the name savegame.sav .

            If the choosen file has no lenght of 45299 the program
            will not work.

            Always use a copy of your savegame.sav file (There are
            10 Slots to save the game in UFO)
@endnode

